{"tid":112892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死2隻]旅遊巴公路撞欄翻側　釀2死29傷","createTime":"2017-02-08T13:47:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T13:14:57.000Z","uid":32407,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bf3c4312cf5b37d58a5207ac217b1a91fe9a8761","tid":112892,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T13:47:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170208/bkncn-20170208203244703-0208_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170208%2Fbkncn-20170208203244703-0208_05011_001.html&d=VPc2G2a59adbLf1ajQMU8tr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=064347fd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170208/bkncn-20170208203244703-0208_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170208/photo/bkncn-20170208203244703-0208_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170208%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170208203244703-0208_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=72306353&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n福建三明市發生致命交通意外，一輛載有54名乘客的大型旅遊巴，今日凌晨駛至福銀高速B道的278KM路段時發生碰撞後翻側，造成兩人當場死亡，其餘52名乘客事後送院檢查。截至下午2時，當地醫院已接收了29名受傷乘客，其中1人情況嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n三明市交警表示，今日凌晨1時55分左右，一輛由河南洛陽開往福建泉州的大型旅遊巴，在福銀高速B道278KM路段撞向防護欄後翻側，造成車內1男1女當場死亡，另外52人則送院檢查。<br />\n<br />\n交警指出，福建高速交警部門嚴令禁止大型客運車輛於凌晨2時至5時在高速公路上行駛。惟這宗意外剛好發生在淩晨1點55分左右，距離禁駛的時間非常接近。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719be246648f513c4a46f7813f43c83b26c85255","tid":112892,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T13:51:50.000Z","msg":"兩隻咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e793813205165af89228d2fc0f98e59fa0b10f33","tid":112892,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T14:06:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a991c239ee170627f0af433bc75e6bf32e66cee9","tid":112892,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T14:23:40.000Z","msg":"死極都仲有，死二件=150-2?"},{"pid":"b9adcf052c7ffd1d99b0b03ed0ed031645fe9c30","tid":112892,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:14:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}